description.content:
I am a professional WordPress Developer, Capable of Customization, Designing, Fixing, Debugging, Improving Performance, SEO, WP Installation, Improving Security and much more

Have created, designed, debugged, redesigned, customized many WordPress websites! 

Contact me for more information and get FREE consultation!


Packages:


Debug / Fix / Create - 80$


Fix any problems BUT contact me before placing the order.


Standard WordPress Website: 


WordPress Installation.

Theme Installation.

Theme Customization.

Developing 4-5 number of pages of your choice.


Fully Functional WordPress Website


This Includes Website from scratch

Including 10 pages ( common pages and custom pages of your choice )

Fully functioning E - Commerce 

Payment Integrations ( Paypal, Stripe etc )

Social media integration ( Facebook, Instagram etc )

10-20 product upload

Basic level SEO

Speed optimization

Security improvement 

permalink changes

Plugin Installation

And much more! 


Other Services that I can offer are:

  • Full On Page SEO


I Guarantee you:

  • Customer Satisfaction! 
  • On time Delivery ( mostly before the time )
  • Unlimited Revisions until you are completely Satisfied!

Contact before placing the order

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Theme Customization?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I have done lots of WordPress theme customization ! That wont be a problem.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I would require you to contact me so that I can evaluate the problem and then I would guide you step by step on what I need from you!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be Responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, it will be desktop / tablet / Mobile responsive! It will look good in all devices :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I don't provide hosting but i can recommend you the best one for your business

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you cusomtize existing wordpress site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can customize your existing website and also give a complete makeover! :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you do for 80$?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can fix any issues like css, add images, php small fix, background images, logo issues etc. I would highly recommend that you contact me before placing order! :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do i contact you?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can press contact button OR you can go to this link and you can directly contact me ! :) https://www.fiverr.com/conversations/smtaqimz
